transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan ji boliye madam.
Executive: Good morning sir, Satyadas ji baat kar rahe hain aap?
Customer: Haan haan haan.
Executive: Sir main Anshika baat kar rahi hu servicing ke regarding aapko ye call kiya. Aapne sir ek incoming call ki thi to uske regarding ek ticket open hui hai aapki.
Customer: Incoming?
Executive: Aapne ye call ki thi shayad hamare kisi account manager ko ya Vasundhara ji ko. Vasundhara ji se aapki aapki baat hui thi na?
Customer: Nahi nahi madam nahi nahi nahi nahi maine kisi ko phone nahi kiya.
Executive: Achha incoming ke regarding ek ticket open hui hai sir aapki.
Customer: Nahi nahi.
Executive: Achha, theek hai. To abhi services ko sir active kara rahe hain aap?
Customer: Nahi nahi.
Executive: Services to active nahi karaenge, theek hai. Kya issues aa rahe hain sir?
Customer: Madam wo ye baar baar baat karna theek nahi rehta hai. Main wo mana kar diya to mana kar diya. Har baar wo teen baar baat karna theek nahi rehta.
Executive: Theek hai sir koi baat nahi.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer states he did not make any call.

- Customer does not want to activate services.

- Customer does not want to be called repeatedly.



Resolution:

- Executive acknowledged the customer's concerns.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None
